<br>
But the other day I ran by a guy named Patiofurniture. <br>
<br>
Hehe, the damn thing is just stuck in my conscious now, why why why? It's not like I'm going to petition or anything, I mean, if he wants to name himself Patiofurniture he can, not my business, but why? Won't stop running through my head picturing this guy sitting at the name selector and choosing...Patiofurniture. hehe<br>
/boggled little Halfling here <p>Laraly Muddlefoot<br>
